<h1>Fonts and icons</h1>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p><a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Chewy?query=chewy"
      target="flatchat_workshop">Google Fonts - Chewy</a></p>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Add to <code>&lt;head&gt;</code></p>
<pre>
&lt;link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Chewy" rel="stylesheet"&gt;
</pre>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Add bottom of 'application.css':</p>
<pre>
.message_body { font-family: 'Chewy', cursive; }
</pre>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p><a href="http://fontawesome.io"
      target="flatchat_workshop">Font Awesome</a></p>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Add to <code>&lt;head&gt;</code></p>
<pre>
&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/font-awesome-4.6.3/css/font-awesome.min.css"&gt;
</pre>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Replace <code>&lt;h3&gt;Rooms&lt;/h3&gt;</code> with:</p>
<pre>
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;i class="fa fa-users"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Rooms&lt;/h3&gt;
</pre>
<p>Add icon 'fa-comments-o' to <code>&lt;h3&gt;Messages&lt;/h3&gt;</code>.</p>
